cadd5a27e72cf522","tid":26752,"uid":37759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T05:02:51.000Z","msg":"睇新聞唔自己去睇原source，等d職業打手西過貼上forum先睇已經係智障<br />\n<br />\n我就係話緊通街都係處呢類人，我唔會亂屌人係廢青毒撚，但就算係冗員我都未見有人等閒到可以除左訓外12小時不時咁出post<br />\n<br />\n另外，上得forum就一定有唔同意見，嘈係必意，唔撚想嘈想舒服，你就等於自動方棄抗爭嘅權力。連打鍼鍵盤戰都懶得打仲信你地會上街抗爭? 不了。<br />\n<br />\n所以話你地廢就係咁解。"},{"pid":"cf6befec0857074dc76e6bd0fe420ed3c8c58ab5","tid":26752,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T05:03:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>香肛又係咁<br />\n御理又係咁<br />\n佐倉又係咁<br />\n一個二個都唔聽既話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係你地先會覺得上網要人指揮既啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你連指揮自己都做唔到啦<br />\n又話退出高登咪又伸返個龜頭出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfd3b221944388bd99de6ce1fe80b6a29a015b00","tid":26752,"uid":1096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T05:05:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>政事台 = 青政時事台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   <br />\n<br />\n唔準講游BB壞話"},{"pid":"e0221931402a4cb1d6bb0559b615a75fc913e5b4","tid":26752,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T05:08:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>政事台 = 青政時事台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你自己過去望下屌緊邊個先啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea1c957028a7e6995b25938a9f26fad675361440","tid":26752,"uid":24547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T05:10:53.000Z","msg":"Op有冇諗過3年後如果熱青本三個黨收晒皮or無討論價值同時又出左熱血青年and 公民新政 到時又時又互屌咁個青政本民前台要改名的問題<br />\n所以用政事台le個名係因為可以長用"},{"pid":"403a3a82d10179172438bf1d2a0a1d4c30b2ae74","tid":26752,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T05:16:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>( Show Blocked User - 溡脇綾香BB )<br />\n<br />\n又block多隻五毛熱狗私怨分化撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"d57bb9aa99ea91ecff2c45f558ee3c825e29b4a9","tid":26752,"uid":37759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T06:22:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>講起洪非凡，雨革個時日日屌左膠，又唔見有人話佢係5毛 ???<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後班左膠扮埋青狗屌洪非凡係5毛，跟住就成班人一齊起鬨，真係唔知咩人淨係識聽人ORDER 回 POST囉咁就。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nP.S.之後又會出現幾羅禮士/安魂曲之流等，低質冇內容洗版式回覆</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n759打手post呢佢係近一年越來越過份先睇得去佢五毛手法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n得罪講句，踩正仇家就拍手叫好，踩正自己就話過份，呢D野我一早睇透，洪非凡我都試過同佢嘈熱血貓民嘈到好勁，但有朝一日佢洗版式開熱血拖我都唔會大叫扑鳩佢。<br />\n<br />\n其實扑人=掩耳盜鈴，你係耳根清靜左，但同時你又會得少左資訊，即使係你唔鐘意聽都好。<br />\n<br />\n正如之前兩次撐釋法集會，你睇淨係睇蘋果等飯民報紙，只會覺得全部都係收錢出黎。但我兩次都係現場做採訪，我好肯定咁講兩次個度都起碼有一半人係自己出黎。<br />\n<br />\n由其第二次撞正英國文化節，真係有成班黃絲底呢頭食完FISH AND CHIPS之後就行去個頭撐DQ糧油。<br />\n<br />\n所以要BLOCK就隨便BLOCK，不過BLOCK得越多就越係圍爐越係井底之蛙越失敗。"}]}